93
00:06:45,072 --> 00:06:46,323
Anong klaseng kalokohan 'yan?

94
00:06:47,074 --> 00:06:48,784
Kung hahayaan natin itong matapos
nang may sampal sa kanyang pulso,

95
00:06:48,867 --> 00:06:50,994
